@startuml
title Activity 1: Add Customer (Base CRM)
start
:Open "Add Customer" form;
:Enter name, email, company, phone, status;
if (All required fields valid?) then (yes)
  :Create customer record;
  :Show success message;
  :Redirect to Customers list;
else (no)
  :Show error message;
  :Stay on form;
endif
stop

