title Activity 2: Save Customer to SQLite (Extension)
start
:Receive POST /customers/add;
:Validate input;
if (valid?) then (yes)
  :Insert customer into SQLite DB;
  :Commit transaction;
  :Redirect to /customers;
else (no)
  :Return error + redirect back;
endif
stop
@enduml